{"tid":2320283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"割席華為｜ 法國球星 基沙文： 應譴責大規模迫害維吾爾族行為","createTime":"2020-12-10T16:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T20:58:11.000Z","uid":227801,"like":124,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"19a9356dd967d164093e6bb290bd91e6e0229595","tid":2320283,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:26:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201210/YCKSLFHYIBBPBIBLQSWYNTWIMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201210%2FYCKSLFHYIBBPBIBLQSWYNTWIMQ%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f19689be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201210%2FYCKSLFHYIBBPBIBLQSWYNTWIMQ%2F&h=ada3a573\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201210/YCKSLFHYIBBPBIBLQSWYNTWIMQ/</a><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n自2017年起為華為拍攝廣告，作為華為手機長期代言人法國球星的基沙文，在華為涉嫌參與有份監視維吾爾族的報道曝光後，在IG上發帖作出終止合作的決定：「在強烈懷疑華為涉及發展有關監視維吾爾族的臉部辨識系統後，我立即與該公司終止了合作關係。」<br />\n「我想借此機會邀請華為，不應只是否認相關指控，更應該盡快採取行動，譴責這種大規模的迫害，並利用它的影響力，為尊重人權的社會作出貢戲。」<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"30b33af1c51210a0fdc2c7bd4ab65177fa760b88","tid":2320283,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"手足"},{"pid":"bcba76b27e885f6ae81bd58065e196c0f66a9ab0","tid":2320283,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5faf0aae99dea1a548a93e679f131792356c40e","tid":2320283,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.